Author: bruno_guy
Text: Im kinda in the same boat as you, I have symptoms of orthorexia too, everything that i eat as to be healthy and i cant eat anything "unhealthy" because it will make me gain weight even tho im only eating like 180 or 200 cals of it I still feel bad and anything that's really high in cal i cant eat and it is hard to overcome it. I still have no good tips and still is not overcoming it but sooner or later i know it will get better sorry I can't help but I hope you just don't feel alone!
